{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_01","textHome":"我叫环彩羽。因为刚来神滨市不久……@对神滨市了解的不是很透彻，@若是彼此间互有不熟悉的，希望能多多交流。@啊！话说……我的兴趣是做料理。@可以的话……我做晚饭给你吃好不好呀？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_18","textHome":"即使如今已经不是了，有朝一日@我也想向小忧坦白……曾经怯懦的自己。@因为我相信……小忧的话，@无论是怎样的我，都会温柔接纳的吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_19","textHome":"为了找回自己重要的东西……@我一定会一次又一次地变强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_20","textHome":"接受弱小的自己……@从这里开始慢慢进步就好了吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_21","textHome":"开始一点点……慢慢改变了吗……？@即便厌恶过去的自己……也不能当作不存在……@应该接纳它，然后超越它……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_22","textHome":"和大家相遇之后，我终于明白了。@正因是重要的人，才不能隐藏自己的本心……@正因为重要，才必须传达出自己真实的心意。@因为对喜欢的人，是不应该说谎的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_23","textHome":"我不会再蒙混过关，也不会再欺骗自己了。@从自我保护的那层厚壳中飞出来后……@发现外面的世界好明亮，感觉浑身都轻松了。@我终于……成为了自己想要成为的人。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.1,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_24","textHome":"昨天也好热啊，你没事吧？@没有出现苦夏症状吧？@可不能一直开着空调哦？@啊……我怎么像个老阿姨似的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_25","textHome":"我好喜欢夏天的清晨啊……@总觉得神清气爽……小学的时候也是……@去跳广播体操时，沿途都很舒爽，@我特别喜欢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_26","textHome":"这个时间段果然很热啊……你还有食欲吗？@嗯～我们尽量选中华凉面之类的……@清爽的食物当午饭吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_27","textHome":"太阳下山后……虽然稍微凉快了一点，@但还是很热呢。啊……我可以去趟超市吗？@我得去买冰淇淋。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_03","textHome":"小忧她无论何时……@都有办法让大家露出笑容呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_28","textHome":"今天也好热啊……@但是总不能就这么开着空调睡觉吧。@啊……我记得八千代说有冰枕来着……@我要不要也试试呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_29","textHome":"你了解星座吗？不是有夏季大三角吗？@我一直都不知道是哪个，总是东张西望地找。@下次教教我吧？我会很开心的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_30","textHome":"出门前要涂防晒霜！@我被晒过之后皮肤会变红……@所以不好好涂防晒，是会出大事的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":300}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_31","textHome":"鹤乃她啊，@暑假期间每天都会去镜之魔女的宅邸……@噗……八千代说……这还真是个省钱的消遣。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_32","textHome":"夏季集中补习！呵呵，我开玩笑的。@趁着夏天天黑得晚，我们一起加倍努力吧？@等到秋天来临的时候……@我们一定，就能强到让别人刮目相看的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":401,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_33","textHome":"阿嚏！是不是因为吹空调吹得太久了啊。@我稍微有点冷。诶嘿嘿……@要小心热伤风哦？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_34","textHome":"我一直以来……都只有学校指定的泳装。@这样的泳装我还是第一次穿……@会、会不会很奇怪？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":301}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_35","textHome":"穿上可爱的泳装之后，就好想去海边啊。@啊！去泳池也不错耶。@我喜欢泳池很多的水上乐园。@……这样会不会太贪心了？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_36","textHome":"自、自由调研啊？我想研究一下……@身边各种食物的糖分、盐分含量。@会、会不会很无聊？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":8.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":301}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_37","textHome":"那个……暑假作业……你做完了吗？@唔……数、数学练习册里面……@有一题我怎么都解不出来……@你、你能不能教教我……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":301}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_04","textHome":"连我都开始说教别人了……@自己都有点难以置信……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.6,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_38","textHome":"我和大家约好了，下次一起去海边。@菲莉希亚她……铆足了劲说要抓鲨鱼……@海、海边应该不会有那种东西吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":200}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_39","textHome":"对了对了，最新一期的杂志上啊，@刊登了八千代的泳装特辑哦！@沙滩裙啊……连体泳衣啊……@哪件她穿着都很好看！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_40","textHome":"你已经准备好泳圈了吗？还有……沙滩拖鞋。@还有还有……野餐布也得带上！@呵呵，能一起去海边，我好期待啊。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_03_41","textHome":"呀啊！我、我在发呆……吓了我一跳。@呵呵，下次我要不要也拿一瓶冰饮料……@啪叽一下贴在你脖子上，吓吓你呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_42","textHome":"一定……没问题……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_43","textHome":"还好没放弃……！"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_44","textHome":"没问题的……我相信！"}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_45","textHome":"姐姐赢了哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_46","textHome":"是不是变成了厉害的姐姐了呢？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_63","textHome":"通往希望……未来……之路！！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.7,"chara":[{"id":100100,"motion":400}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_05","textHome":"果然……这两人不在的话感觉就少了些什么。@两位……欢迎回来。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":100}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_64","textHome":"愿这一箭……化为通向未来的道路！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_65","textHome":"思念着想要守护之人的心情……@现在成为我的力量！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":1}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100100,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1001_00_66","textHome":"结束吧……不会再让任何人悲伤了！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100100,"motion":400}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":1